   "len": 52,
   "en": "$N looks at $Y. \"You haven't any room in your pack.\"",
   "zh": "$N看了看$Y。「汝的背包已無空間。」",
   "note": "action；inventory full"
  },
  {
   "offset": 2339,
   "len": 45,
   "en": "\"I'm afraid you haven't enough money for it.\"",
   "zh": "「恐怕汝的金幣不夠。」",
   "note": "insufficient gold（重複）"
  },
  {
