   "zh": "$N將口糧遞給$Y。",
   "note": "action"
  },
  {
   "offset": 2469,
   "len": 31,
   "en": "He hands $Y #9 mutton ration\\s.",
   "zh": "他將#9份羊肉口糧遞給$Y。",
   "note": "action；#9 = quantity variable；\\s = plural suffix"
  },
  {
   "offset": 2507,
   "len": 27,
   "en": "\"That's all you can carry.\"",
   "zh": "「這是汝所能攜帶的上限了。」",
   "note": "carry limit"
  },
  {
   "offset": 2543,
